{"tid":2066163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見大家對前刑事檢控專員阮雲道有興趣,順便一講","createTime":"2020-06-16T06:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T07:54:39.000Z","uid":26770,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1cf8d541b3203a7e7621b57438fc2207ff1a94a1","tid":2066163,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T06:02:53.000Z","msg":"我無打錯<br />\n<ins>阮雲道係1994-1997撈刑事檢控專員</ins><br />\n<br />\n接任阮雲道的係<ins>洋五毛江樂士</ins>,現在狂支持惡法同合理化警暴<br />\n現任咪係<span style=\"color: red;\">堅持要屈到荃灣警局輪姦案受害人坐監</span>去滅聲的刑事檢控專員 <ins>豬狗不如梁卓然</ins><br />\n-------------------------------------------------<br />\n阮雲道任內最大污點就係其子阮嘉輝藏毒<br />\n如果疑犯係公屋租客,慣例doj一定釘死<br />\n<strong>但阮雲道曾任刑事檢控專員根本無人敢釘</strong><br />\n--------------------------------------------------------<br />\n歷代刑事檢控專員就係東廠廠公<br />\n由英治時期的David Boy QC到現在的現在的梁卓然都係<br />\n專幫政權做dirty work, 梁卓然係共產黨的牌位係高過鄭若驊"},{"pid":"8aaf57bf93530d15c70de4e80ba104885cac8915","tid":2066163,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T06:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3305980aab95bcb8c9a8c6fe74c2b82278e51a","tid":2066163,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T06:05:53.000Z","msg":"對於阮雲道其子暴斃一案<br />\n好多人話係報應<br />\n'你老豆同世叔伯縱容你,天收你'<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但我會講係阮家業力爆發</span>"},{"pid":"f4ace1fb7d8705a31939449852c37950981197e5","tid":2066163,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"阮家輝係細仔<br />\n與兄長在美國Boston讀書<br />\n<br />\n全家應該死剩長子"},{"pid":"c4cd44fda25d63f34dc2d4fa1d4781b88e57fe10","tid":2066163,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4ace1fb7d8705a31939449852c37950981197e5","tid":2066163,"uid":26770,"like"